{"tid":2131008,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美心集團旗下迪士尼員工餐廳 ODV 一廚師確診　餐廳本獲豁免現關閉三日　","createTime":"2020-07-29T14:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T05:45:16.000Z","uid":5195,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b726236b5c8cd2e2c637764b6c41ffb69519d35f","tid":2131008,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:03:23.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情肆虐，本港現時部份員工餐廳獲政府豁免，仍然可提供堂食。有消息人士向《立場新聞》透露，由美心集團管理、迪士尼員工餐廳「ODV」近日一名員工確診，任職廚師，負責餐廳食物製作、收貨等工作。消息指，確診者其家人早前已經確診，該公司獲悉後在 7 月 20 日已要求該員工隔離 14 日，然後在隔離第九日即今日確診，餐廳明日起停業三日，下周一重新營業。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，有關的迪士尼員工餐廳獲政府豁免，客源包括迪士尼員工、地盤工人、送貨工人等。消息人士反映，確診員工在隔離前曾與多名員工接觸，亦有製作食物，工作期間經常除下口罩，但批評美心集團未有將事件向外界公布，且亦未有為其他員工安排檢測，或安排有需要的員工在家隔離。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》正就事件向美心集團查詢，暫時未有回覆。"},{"pid":"21c18d02ab0dd7e4014984ad3743ce745123b32c","tid":2131008,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0037e34841fd74075ff304fbf1cd82197b4ea9eb","tid":2131008,"uid":17473,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:10:39.000Z","msg":"迪士尼群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da7a0b6b90bd8e009c7c8a45433b7a676ab5670","tid":2131008,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:11:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac618355fbc54b756b38abeb72ccd99b4b89c51e","tid":2131008,"uid":148494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc8e3784662076f3eb9caffc0cb28c4f897e466","tid":2131008,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:25:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iH7x2C5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiH7x2C5.jpg&h=f2dfda94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b767dcede92423e0ef18fb1ea2db7aa6ea4d08b0","tid":2131008,"uid":54516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:28:50.000Z","msg":"又係黑心，都唔知黑心有幾多單確診未對外公布。"},{"pid":"cbc16188d7addeee01204b2e285965cb9bc7138f","tid":2131008,"uid":17473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:01:01.000Z","msg":"員工幾千個，唔知點收科<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5380a442cc13c48fa497b7cd0e23ea8439ad18","tid":2131008,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:07:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05279d5123ea955e3609fd00c9d01c0ce3e1aacf","tid":2131008,"uid":17473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T05:45:16.000Z","msg":"得立場一間報出黎，電視新聞都冇講"}]}